Description: This package contains the snirf2bids function, a GUI that can be used to convert raw fNIRS recordings in snirf-format to a BIDS-compliant dataset.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
Import: shiny, bslib, here, tidyr, bslib, here, DT, stringr, purrr, dplyr, BiocManager, datamods
